headline: Novocure Stock Earns 96 RS Rating
summary: On Tuesday, Novocure[ticker symb=NVCR] stock got a positive adjustment to its Relative Strength (RS) Rating, from 73 to 96. The oncology company had some good news Monday announcing success in its pancreatic cancer study.
